#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.empty.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.empty"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:1 of
msgid "Return a new tensor of given shape and type, without initializing entries."
msgstr "返回一个给定形状和类型的张量，不初始化其元素。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:3 of
msgid "Shape of the empty tensor"
msgstr "空张量的形状"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:5 of
msgid "Desired output data-type."
msgstr "期望的输出数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:7 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:9 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:11 of
msgid ""
"Whether to store multi-dimensional data in row-major (C-style) or column-"
"major (Fortran-style) order in memory."
msgstr "是否以行优先（C 风格）或列优先（Fortran 风格）的方式在内存中存储多维数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:16 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Tensor of uninitialized (arbitrary) data of the given shape, "
"dtype, and order.  Object arrays will be initialized to None."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 给定形状、数据类型和顺序的未初始化（任意）数据的张量。对象数组"
"将被初始化为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`empty_like`, :py:obj:`zeros`, :py:obj:`ones`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:23 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty:24 of
msgid ""
"`empty`, unlike `zeros`, does not set the array values to zero, and may "
"therefore be marginally faster.  On the other hand, it requires the user "
"to manually set all the values in the array, and should be used with "
"caution."
msgstr ""
"`empty` 与 `zeros` 不同，它不会将数组值设置为零，因此可能略微快一些。"
"另一方面，它要求用户手动设置数组中的所有值，应谨慎使用。"

